{"parse":{"title":"green onion","pageid":199808,"redirects":[],"wikitext":"==English==\n\n===Noun===\n{{en-noun}}\n\n# {{lb|en|North America}} {{synonym of|en|spring onion}}.\n{{attention|en|Pretty sure we use \"green onion\" in Australia too but I've always been unsure about what is what regarding shallots, green onions, scallions, chives, Welsh onions, etc.}}\n\n{{C|en|Alliums}}"}}